The '''Duros Cultural Center''' (DCC) was the primary gathering place for those [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] who were living on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the decades leading up to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The DCC was located in the [[Boribos Prefecture]] at the time.

